Many basketball supporters can agree that basketball an all year around sport. In the light of basketball being an all year around sport, the travel season is approaching us very quickly. In the travel season, you often see a different type of basketball than school ball and it is exciting to watch how the girls play in a different basketball setting. At Prep Girls Hoop Oklahoma, we understand and believe that basketball is an all year around sport in which we aim to provide coverage for all high school girls basketball players. The first evaluation period is coming at the end of April, here are some upcoming events a few Oklahoma teams to be on the lookout for and some of the players that make up their rosters.

